{
  "annotations": { "list": [] },
  "editable": true,
  "graphTooltip": 0,
  "schemaVersion": 39,
  "title": "Conexão Solidária — Aplicação",
  "tags": ["conexao-solidaria", "aplicacao"],
  "templating": {
    "list": [
      {
        "name": "datasource",
        "type": "datasource",
        "query": "prometheus",
        "current": {},
        "hide": 0
      },
      {
        "name": "job",
        "type": "query",
        "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
        "query": "label_values(http_server_request_duration_seconds_count, job)",
        "includeAll": true,
        "multi": true,
        "current": { "text": "All", "value": "$__all" }
      }
    ]
  },
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Requests/s por serviço",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 0 },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "reqps" }, "overrides": [] },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
          "expr": "sum by (job) (rate(http_server_request_duration_seconds_count{job=~\"$job\"}[5m]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{job}}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Latência p95 (s)",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 0 },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "s" }, "overrides": [] },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, sum by (le, job) (rate(http_server_request_duration_seconds_bucket{job=~\"$job\"}[5m])))",
          "legendFormat": "{{job}}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Respostas 5xx/s",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 8 },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "reqps" }, "overrides": [] },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
          "expr": "sum by (job) (rate(http_server_request_duration_seconds_count{job=~\"$job\", http_response_status_code=~\"5..\"}[5m]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{job}}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "Métricas de fila / DLQ",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 8 },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "**Service Bus (fila/DLQ):** profundidade da subscription e contagem de DLQ vêm do **Azure Monitor** (métricas do namespace do Service Bus), não do `/metrics` das APIs. Plugar o data source Azure Monitor no Grafana e adicionar os painéis `ActiveMessages` / `DeadletteredMessages` por entidade (`donation-requested`, `payment-result`). _Follow-up — RNF29._\n\nO **lag de consolidação** (pagamento aprovado → ValorArrecadado) é observável pelas métricas OTel da DonationAPI."
      }
    }
  ]
}
